OL,3,CHouseholds urged to spend Boxing Day
OL,4,Cusing up Christmas leftovers
OL,6,FHouseholds have been urged to spend
OL,7,FBoxing Day using up Christmas dinner
OL,8,Fleftovers amid figures suggesting food
OL,9,Fwaste will cost a family of four an
OL,10,Faverage of #1,000 this year.
OL,12,FHouseholds are set to throw away
OL,13,Faround 85,000 tonnes of edible
OL,14,FChristmas food this festive season
OL,15,Falone, according to estimates from the
OL,16,FWaste and Resources Action Programme
OL,17,F(Wrap) and the Office for National
OL,18,FStatistics.
