OL,3,CHouseholds urged to spend Boxing Day
OL,4,Cusing up Christmas leftovers
OL,6,FSome 16 million tonnes of CO2 are
OL,7,Fgenerated by UK homes from wasted
OL,8,Fconsumable food and drink each year,
OL,9,FWrap said.
OL,11,FThroughout the year, almost 40% of
OL,12,Ffood waste happens because it is not
OL,13,Fused in time ` either because people
OL,14,Fthink the product smells or looks off
OL,15,For it is past its date label, a study
OL,16,Ffor the organisation found.
OL,18,FEach year, UK households threw out
OL,19,F480,000 tonnes of potatoes ` or 41% of
OL,20,Fall potatoes bought.
