OL,3,CHouseholds urged to spend Boxing Day
OL,4,Cusing up Christmas leftovers
OL,6,FWrap has urged households to store
OL,7,Fpotatoes ` and all other uncut fruit
OL,8,Fand vegetables except for onions,
OL,9,Fbananas and whole pineapples ` in the
OL,10,Ffridge at 5C or below.
OL,12,FIt also reminded consumers that food
OL,13,Fpast its 'best before' date is safe to
OL,14,Feat for days, months or even years
OL,15,Fafterwards, and people should use
OL,16,Ftheir own judgment to decide if their
OL,17,Ffood is edible.
OL,19,FHowever, 'use by' labels refer to
OL,20,Fsafety, and food should not be eaten
OL,21,Fpast this date.
