OL,3,CHouseholds urged to spend Boxing Day
OL,4,Cusing up Christmas leftovers
OL,6,FCircular economy minister Mary Creagh
OL,7,Fsaid: "Over half of food waste happens
OL,8,Fin our homes so reheating extra
OL,9,Froasties and making the traditional
OL,10,Fturkey curry can save money and cut
OL,11,Fcarbon emissions.
OL,13,F"Together with the Government's #13.5
OL,14,Fmillion grants to food charities to
OL,15,Fredistribute 19,000 tonnes of surplus
OL,16,Ffood from farms, small changes can
OL,17,Fmake the Christmas food shop go
OL,18,Ffurther and end up in the freezer not
OL,19,Fthe food waste caddy."
