OL,3,CHouseholds urged to spend Boxing Day
OL,4,Cusing up Christmas leftovers
OL,6,FThe focus on food waste comes as
OL,7,Fappliance brands launch built-in AI
OL,8,Ftools to help consumers use up the
OL,9,Fcontents of their fridges and freezers.
OL,11,FHisense's ConnectLife app now features
OL,12,FDish Designer, which uses AI to create
OL,13,Fcustomised recipes from the contents
OL,14,Fof its fridges and freezers ` a
OL,15,Fsimilar feature to Samsung's Bespoke
OL,16,FAI fridge freezers which have
OL,17,Ftouchscreen displays that generate
OL,18,Frecipes, largely by scanning what is
OL,19,Finside the fridge.
