OL,3,CHouseholds urged to spend Boxing Day
OL,4,Cusing up Christmas leftovers
OL,6,FHisense's Dish Designer can
OL,7,Fpersonalise recipes depending on
OL,8,Fhouseholds' dietary requirements, and
OL,9,Fmembers can add products in the fridge
OL,10,Fand cupboards to an 'inventory', which
OL,11,Fis used to generate recipes.
OL,13,FHisense said approximately 30,000
OL,14,Frecipes had been generated in total
OL,15,Facross Europe since Dish Designer
OL,16,Flaunched in May.
OL,18,FOf these, around 12,000 recipes were
OL,19,Fgenerated in the UK.
